<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='416:439'>或問曰洛書云一曰水二曰火三曰木四曰金五曰土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='439:462'>則與龍圖五行之數之位不偶者何也答曰此謂陳其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='462:485'>生數也且雖則陳其生數乃是已交之數也下篇分土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='485:508'>王四季則備其成數矣且夫洛書九疇惟出於五行之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='508:531'>數故先陳其已交之生數然後以土數足之乃可見其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='531:536'>成數也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='536:562'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0011', 'WYG', '003-5a' );" name="003-5a" class="pb">[003-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
